description: Low temperature series for spin-1/2 Ising magnetic susceptibility on 4D simple cubic lattice (divided by 4).
references: S. R. Finch, Mathematical Constants, Cambridge, 2003, pp. 391-406.

C. Vohwinkel and P. Weisz, Low-temperature expansion in the d=4 Ising model, Nucl. Phys. B 374 (1992) 647-666.
author: _Steven Finch_
